{
  "3004390": {
    "name": "The Cave Diver",
    "steam_appid": 3004390,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>洞穴中令人窒息的岩石正慢慢闭合，夺走又一个灵魂。</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>继续爬行……</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>终有一道通路会打开……</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>在幽闭恐惧的隧道和无情的岔路中爬行。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004390/extras/08483dd5e3d28fdfbf47f06f0fe71929.poster.avif?t=1771348593\" width=608 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004390/extras/08483dd5e3d28fdfbf47f06f0fe71929.webm?t=1771348593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004390/extras/08483dd5e3d28fdfbf47f06f0fe71929.mp4?t=1771348593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这些洞穴是由压迫性的岩石和狭窄通道组成的迷宫。分叉的隧道会诱导你进入幽闭的死胡同，在那里，回头已然不可能。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>通过多次尝试绘制洞穴系统的地图。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004390/extras/cd866d216d5b4b2e58efb6e3c98f12b2.poster.avif?t=1771348593\" width=608 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004390/extras/cd866d216d5b4b2e58efb6e3c98f12b2.webm?t=1771348593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004390/extras/cd866d216d5b4b2e58efb6e3c98f12b2.mp4?t=1771348593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在岩石上钉上粗糙的标志，以追踪你深入洞穴的路径。每一具新尸体出现后，洞穴便变得更加熟悉。那些先来者留下的痕迹依然存在……</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>不要被困住。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004390/extras/8d0e2020d53dd31f0fe314e36e53d81f.poster.avif?t=1771348593\" width=608 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004390/extras/8d0e2020d53dd31f0fe314e36e53d81f.webm?t=1771348593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004390/extras/8d0e2020d53dd31f0fe314e36e53d81f.mp4?t=1771348593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这洞穴并非活人之地。被困就意味着孤独地死去，被封于岩石之中。没有人会来救你。当你以新的洞穴探险者身份归来时，也许会偶然发现你前任腐烂的尸体——如果你能找到的话。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>学会穿越物理谜题。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004390/extras/6f1d63be42796f1357be6a20449ad328.poster.avif?t=1771348593\" width=608 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004390/extras/6f1d63be42796f1357be6a20449ad328.webm?t=1771348593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004390/extras/6f1d63be42796f1357be6a20449ad328.mp4?t=1771348593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >掌握双手的动作与抓握技巧，小心地穿越障碍并解开基于物理的谜题。每一个动作都需通过失败来精进。只有那些执着的、耐心的、疯狂的人才能深入下去。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>发现地底深处隐藏的恐怖。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004390/extras/c447461217d0e921a436fd4e31c5b7da.poster.avif?t=1771348593\" width=608 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004390/extras/c447461217d0e921a436fd4e31c5b7da.webm?t=1771348593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3004390/extras/c447461217d0e921a436fd4e31c5b7da.mp4?t=1771348593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >几代人以来，你的家族一直流传着一种稀有花朵的传说，它生长在这些洞穴的最深处。据说，这朵花能治愈一切疾病——甚至是双腿瘫痪。但每一个进入洞穴的人都未能返回……有人说，是洞穴本身将他们吞噬……还有人说，在地下深处，有某种古老的存在正在蠢蠢欲动——那是比人类更古老的邪恶……</p>",
